ering I had no clue what Gay was, or what sexuality even was at all. I imagine I would have developed several crushes on boys at the time, just like I did on different girls. What im trying to say I guess here is, I just naturally was attracted to women from very early on in my life. I had no clue or care what so ever as to weather or not I was making a CHOICE, at all, my choice was simply made by my hormons and desires at that time. I have a good enough imagination to believe that had I been attracted to boys at that time, I would now be gay. I dont believe its a choice at all, I believe its what sexually drives you, and it happens from a very early time in your life. Now if you never had a sexual impulse what so ever untill age 15, and at that time you then were given a choice where to unleash your hormons to, then I might believe its a choice.<br>
